WEBVTT

00:00.174 --> 00:05.122
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:06.094 --> 00:08.802
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.934 --> 00:13.942
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.966 --> 00:18.722
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.758 --> 00:22.786
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.790 --> 00:27.734
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.758 --> 00:31.030
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:31.054 --> 00:34.518
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.542 --> 00:39.790
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.790 --> 00:41.408
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.408 --> 00:44.886
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.910 --> 00:48.182
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.206 --> 00:53.878
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.902 --> 00:55.246
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.246 --> 00:58.582
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.606 --> 01:01.954
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:02.062 --> 01:07.259
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.259 --> 01:08.942
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.942 --> 01:12.342
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.366 --> 01:15.766
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.790 --> 01:21.366
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.390 --> 01:24.802
♪ I love you ♪

01:27.080 --> 01:27.870
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.870 --> 01:31.122
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 27=

01:31.710 --> 01:34.418
(Qiang Qingci will never leave.)

01:41.266 --> 01:43.846
- He won't let me eat it.
- You eat it raw?

01:44.786 --> 01:46.047
Don't talk to me!

01:46.947 --> 01:48.242
Does it smell good?

01:53.747 --> 01:55.566
You know what it's like to be ignored?

01:56.426 --> 02:00.927
If you know you're ignored,
then accept it.

02:05.066 --> 02:06.086
Here.

02:22.226 --> 02:24.207
- Need help?
- I'm fine.

02:31.386 --> 02:35.326
- Okay, next.
- Come on, next.

02:37.027 --> 02:38.322
- You're back!
- You're back!

02:38.346 --> 02:39.446
We're back!

02:40.987 --> 02:44.322
- What a nice smell!
- Calm down a bit.

02:44.346 --> 02:46.563
You will smell this fragrance all night.

02:46.587 --> 02:48.886
- Mr. Mo is cooking pig's feet.
- Really?

02:49.907 --> 02:51.606
I'm so hungry!

02:51.907 --> 02:55.642
It seems like
we can't use the kitchen today.

02:55.666 --> 02:57.446
Certainly not.

02:59.666 --> 03:03.322
- Then we can order some skewers.
- Skewers! Nice!

03:03.346 --> 03:06.006
- Right?
- Who wants to order skewers?

03:06.226 --> 03:07.467
- Mao!
- Order more!

03:07.467 --> 03:09.163
- Order more, seriously!
- We're starving.

03:09.187 --> 03:11.446
Your hearings are really sharp.

03:11.826 --> 03:16.826
Only skewers can make up for our pain
of seeing but not being able to eat.

03:16.826 --> 03:18.846
You can smell them before we even order?

03:20.546 --> 03:21.883
Why has the chef come out?

03:21.907 --> 03:25.087
Two stoves, simmer for an hour.
I'll take a little rest.

03:25.427 --> 03:28.046
The chef also wants to eat barbecue,
huh?

03:36.427 --> 03:39.207
You haven't slept much this week,
have you?

03:40.066 --> 03:41.927
- It's alright.
- It's okay.

03:42.307 --> 03:45.482
What do you think?
It's not easy to be the chief director!

03:45.506 --> 03:46.807
Chief planner.

03:54.106 --> 03:56.046
- It smells good.
- Here.

04:03.066 --> 04:04.367
Done.

04:12.067 --> 04:15.246
- It's ready to be served.
- Okay, I'll go get the lunch box.

04:19.267 --> 04:20.486
Wanna taste it?

04:22.587 --> 04:25.046
I thought you wouldn't
allow me to eat it.

04:26.546 --> 04:28.606
This is a pot
privately kept by the chef.

04:45.387 --> 04:47.806
- Go eat in secret.
- Okay.

05:05.786 --> 05:07.926
It's delicious, just a bit spicy.

05:08.866 --> 05:10.887
There's no rice left.
I'll get you some water.

05:26.147 --> 05:28.366
Wait until I finish this bite.

05:29.947 --> 05:32.606
If you like it,
I'll cook more for you in the future.

05:33.546 --> 05:37.606
You don't understand. It's most memorable
when you taste it for the first time.

05:40.746 --> 05:43.567
- Eat slowly.
- Do you need...

05:45.267 --> 05:46.267
Help?

05:48.067 --> 05:50.482
You're stealing good food!

05:51.038 --> 05:54.767
This was meant to be your midnight snack.
Hurry up and take it out.

05:54.947 --> 05:56.967
That's better. Take it.

05:57.186 --> 05:59.887
I'll take it away first.
Mu, the chopsticks.

06:01.067 --> 06:03.207
Guys, our midnight snack is here!

06:03.746 --> 06:06.046
- Didn't you say it's not allowed?
- Water.

06:12.186 --> 06:13.327
Have a try.

06:21.507 --> 06:22.686
It's not bad.

06:23.467 --> 06:25.246
Praising yourself, huh?

06:25.866 --> 06:27.606
Don't I deserve to be praised?

06:28.147 --> 06:31.527
You do. You're
the most deserving person in the world.

06:32.866 --> 06:36.606
Eat a bit more. You still have to
work later into the night.

07:01.746 --> 07:05.127
Mao, can you hear me?

07:06.507 --> 07:12.286
- Turn up the feedback volume a little.
- Alright, give me a moment.

07:19.426 --> 07:21.767
- Try it again.
- Okay.

07:22.267 --> 07:25.642
Everyone,
this is our final technical rehearsal.

07:25.666 --> 07:29.087
Let's all cheer up. Let's do it
like it's the real thing, okay?

07:30.587 --> 07:34.162
- Cheer up, okay?
- Okay!

07:34.186 --> 07:35.986
- Okay!
- Okay, Mr. Juemei!

07:35.986 --> 07:36.907
- You're on.
- Okay.

07:36.907 --> 07:37.587
I'll go down there.

07:37.587 --> 07:40.007
- Everyone, get ready.
- I'll listen down there.

07:40.947 --> 07:44.606
- Guai, are you nervous?
- No, I'm excited.

07:44.707 --> 07:50.202
- Good, you are a true master.
- They're all my seniors, I wouldn't dare.

07:50.226 --> 07:54.642
I was excited to watch your Yangshuo live,
busy with bullet chatting

07:54.666 --> 07:57.182
about Zhaozhaomumu Music Studio
and Shengshengman.

07:57.182 --> 08:00.486
I never thought
I'd be sitting on stage today.

08:01.027 --> 08:05.207
This is much bigger
than the one in Yangshuo.

08:07.587 --> 08:11.647
- Just kidding.
- Right. It's a grand gala today.

08:11.786 --> 08:12.887
That's right.

08:13.426 --> 08:14.887
Okay, get ready.

08:15.134 --> 08:17.767
Everyone, get ready.

08:25.466 --> 08:27.686
Let's go. It's time.

08:32.586 --> 08:34.806
Come on, let's take a picture.

08:36.546 --> 08:38.767
That's him!

08:52.867 --> 08:55.042
- This row, thank you.
- That row.

08:55.066 --> 08:56.166
Thank you.

08:59.227 --> 09:01.247
Here!

09:01.306 --> 09:03.086
- Reserve a seat for Gu Sheng.
- OK.

09:04.867 --> 09:06.046
It's so big!

09:06.306 --> 09:07.454
There are so many people!

09:07.454 --> 09:09.162
- So many.
- It's so big and beautiful.

09:09.186 --> 09:11.806
- Look at this.
- Look, there's gauze above.

09:11.998 --> 09:14.446
- It's very traditional.
- The stage is so big.

09:15.173 --> 09:17.314
(Zhou Zheng)

09:17.426 --> 09:19.686
- What's this?
- It's for you. Take it.

09:20.987 --> 09:22.887
Hold it high later.

09:26.507 --> 09:29.363
- Hello.
- Do you sit here?

09:29.387 --> 09:33.247
- There's a song today composed by Sheng.
- Really?

09:34.107 --> 09:36.603
- What's it called?
- It's called Qi Yu.

09:36.627 --> 09:40.966
- I'll tell you when it's time.
- That's great.

09:50.916 --> 09:55.538
(Traditional Music Gala)

10:03.186 --> 10:05.686
The stage design this year
is so beautiful.

10:06.507 --> 10:07.686
Do you like it?

10:08.227 --> 10:08.723
Yes!

10:08.747 --> 10:13.247
Hurry up! Don't delay, I told you!
The show has started, there's no time!

10:13.546 --> 10:15.922
- I'm sorry! Excuse me!
- It's okay. Be careful.

10:15.946 --> 10:17.166
Hurry!

10:17.867 --> 10:19.367
- Are you okay?
- It's fine.

10:23.227 --> 10:26.627
- Good evening to you all!
- It's starting!

10:26.627 --> 10:29.282
I am your host Juemei Shayi.

10:29.306 --> 10:32.376
Welcome to the annual
Traditional Music Gala.

10:32.376 --> 10:35.407
Hope everyone has a wonderful evening.

10:45.666 --> 10:47.206
Heroes in Golden Age!

10:47.747 --> 10:50.926
- Well...
- This is the opening song chosen by vote.

11:05.027 --> 11:08.926
- Wang Ke!
- Linglong!

11:08.958 --> 11:10.334
♪ Stars of last night ♪

11:10.334 --> 11:12.682
♪ Shadow moves in the woods,
so does the wind ♪

11:12.706 --> 11:15.446
Linglong!

11:16.222 --> 11:17.598
♪ Walking on the leaves ♪

11:17.598 --> 11:19.838
♪ Picking flowers as a blade,
like the wind ♪

11:19.838 --> 11:21.182
♪ As told by the later generations ♪

11:21.182 --> 11:23.518
♪ It's last night's dream,
last night's wind ♪

11:23.518 --> 11:24.862
♪ There are so many layers of moonlight ♪

11:24.862 --> 11:27.134
♪ To shine through the world,
but who can own it alone ♪

11:27.134 --> 11:28.723
♪ Ice cold blades ♪

11:28.747 --> 11:30.686
Wang Ke is so handsome!

11:30.750 --> 11:32.168
♪ White horse with silver saddle ♪

11:32.168 --> 11:34.089
♪ Gallops like Metor
through the night sky ♪

11:34.089 --> 11:35.934
♪ It's last night's dream,
last night's wind ♪

11:35.934 --> 11:40.391
♪ Dimly heading back in composure ♪

11:40.574 --> 11:44.752
♪ Laugh and talk about that dream ♪

11:44.752 --> 11:50.802
♪ Last night's guest left
without a trace ♪

11:50.826 --> 11:52.358
I also want that hat!

11:52.382 --> 11:55.966
♪ Drifting in the world,
how many grudges and grievances ♪

11:55.966 --> 11:59.494
♪ Joy and sorrow, partings and reunions,
troubling merely a single year ♪

11:59.494 --> 12:03.230
♪ Right and wrong,
why should the world judge ♪

12:03.230 --> 12:06.782
♪ It's enough that I do what I want ♪

12:06.782 --> 12:10.438
♪ Wandering the world of hero, fighting,
coming and going freely ♪

12:10.438 --> 12:13.627
♪ Behind me,
there are no flowers, nor wine ♪

12:13.627 --> 12:16.446
- Wang Ke!
- Wang Ke!

12:17.726 --> 12:21.746
♪ I see the golden age in my eyes ♪

12:24.426 --> 12:26.206
Linglong!

12:29.666 --> 12:31.926
The feeling of watching live
is really different.

12:39.786 --> 12:42.286
They're on!

12:42.347 --> 12:44.227
- And there's Feishao!
- Feishao!

12:44.227 --> 12:45.326
Feishao!

12:50.782 --> 12:54.142
♪ Stars of last night,
where does the wind suddenly come from ♪

12:54.142 --> 12:58.162
♪ The war never stops, so does the fight ♪

12:58.186 --> 12:59.647
So amazing!

13:01.470 --> 13:05.254
♪ I go with my heart,
with tonight's dream, tonight's wind ♪

13:05.278 --> 13:08.926
♪ They say what goes around comes around ♪

13:08.926 --> 13:12.725
♪ If that holds true,
all enmity in the world comes to an end ♪

13:12.725 --> 13:15.998
♪ Universal peace reigns,
as the smoke of war fades into air ♪

13:15.998 --> 13:17.822
♪ It's tonight's dream, tonight's wind ♪

13:17.822 --> 13:20.347
♪ Dimly heading back in composure ♪

13:20.347 --> 13:22.926
- So beautiful!
- So beautiful!

13:24.306 --> 13:26.367
Her green dress is so beautiful!

13:26.526 --> 13:33.842
♪ A gust vanishes in a fleeting moment,
like a startled swan ♪

13:34.142 --> 13:37.790
♪ Drifting in the world,
how many grudges and grievances ♪

13:37.790 --> 13:41.406
♪ Joy and sorrow, partings and reunions,
troubling merely a single year ♪

13:41.406 --> 13:45.022
♪ Right and wrong,
why should the world judge ♪

13:45.022 --> 13:48.670
♪ It's enough that I do what I want ♪

13:48.670 --> 13:52.384
♪ Wandering the world of hero, fighting,
coming and going freely ♪

13:52.384 --> 13:55.967
♪ Behind me,
there are no flowers, nor wine ♪

13:55.967 --> 13:59.978
♪ Blending into the bustling streets,
looking back as I move aside ♪

14:01.507 --> 14:02.627
So cool!

14:02.627 --> 14:09.568
♪ I travel around,
freely living to my heart's content ♪

14:09.568 --> 14:16.934
♪ Immortal fame is not what I seek ♪

14:16.958 --> 14:24.134
♪ Roaming the world,
fearless of love or hatred ♪

14:24.158 --> 14:32.158
♪ Joy and sorrow, partings and reunions,
troubling merely a single year ♪

14:34.227 --> 14:37.206
Doudou is so beautiful!

14:38.826 --> 14:42.522
Wang Ke! Doudou!

14:42.546 --> 14:43.926
So good!

14:47.946 --> 14:51.723
Doudou! Linglong!

14:51.747 --> 14:55.367
- Linglong!
- Linglong!

15:05.018 --> 15:07.282
(Qi Yu performed by Linglong
Composer: Shengshengman)

15:07.306 --> 15:09.007
- My name is on it!
- Right.

15:13.227 --> 15:16.086
Qi Yu! This is it!

15:18.306 --> 15:22.847
Singing this song for the first time
on this stage shows her fondness for it.

15:23.586 --> 15:27.086
My composition skills are quite good,
Mr. Qiang Qingci.

15:33.662 --> 15:37.458
♪ Behold by riverside ♪

15:37.790 --> 15:41.682
♪ The verdant bamboo so green ♪

15:42.366 --> 15:44.870
♪ Our duke is dignified ♪

15:44.894 --> 15:48.646
♪ Decorating ears with sparkling jewels ♪

15:48.670 --> 15:53.170
♪ The hat is like stars in the sky ♪

15:55.186 --> 15:58.603
I'm even more excited than
when I saw Sheng on stage in Yangshuo.

15:58.627 --> 16:02.042
Of course, she sang harmony last time.
But this is a song she wrote herself,

16:02.066 --> 16:04.562
and Linglong sings.
It certainly feels different!

16:04.586 --> 16:08.483
Also! The music is composed by Sheng,
and the lyrics are proposed by Off Key.

16:08.507 --> 16:10.107
That girl in the folk music ensemble
is Guai.

16:10.107 --> 16:11.747
We've got three people
contributed to the song.

16:11.747 --> 16:13.442
- Which one?
- The one playing the guzheng.

16:13.466 --> 16:15.987
- I was too excited to introduce her.
- That girl! Super cool!

16:15.987 --> 16:17.446
Exactly!

16:17.918 --> 16:22.662
♪ Behold by riverside ♪

16:22.686 --> 16:26.822
♪ Bamboos so lush and green ♪

16:26.846 --> 16:29.438
♪ Our duke is dignified ♪

16:29.438 --> 16:31.102
♪ Like polished ivory ♪

16:31.102 --> 16:34.334
♪ And polished jade ♪

16:34.334 --> 16:39.261
♪ Broad-minded and generous ♪

16:39.285 --> 16:43.442
♪ Calm and composed ♪

16:43.486 --> 16:46.532
♪ Humourous and witty ♪

16:46.532 --> 16:52.498
♪ Without being harsh ♪

16:53.790 --> 16:57.170
♪ Humourous and witty ♪

16:57.470 --> 17:05.470
♪ Without being harsh ♪

17:06.907 --> 17:10.307
At today's fine feast,
our joy is hard to fully express.

17:10.307 --> 17:13.466
The zither sounds lively.
A new song is introduced wonderfully.

17:13.466 --> 17:16.426
- Sheng is incredible!
- Thanks for the song Linglong brought us,

17:16.426 --> 17:18.587
- the dreamlike Qi Yu.
- So beautiful!

17:18.587 --> 17:20.087
It's well written, too.

17:20.287 --> 17:22.578
- Let's enjoy the next performance.
- Let's head backstage.

17:24.946 --> 17:28.327
- Off Key!
- Sheng!

17:29.107 --> 17:30.446
Did you just see that?

17:31.067 --> 17:35.763
It's just wonderful!
Miss Linglong is truly stunning!

17:35.787 --> 17:37.807
- Mr. Mo.
- Alright.

17:38.067 --> 17:40.843
- Are you ready to go on stage?
- The next one.

17:40.867 --> 17:42.127
Don't be nervous.

17:42.347 --> 17:44.523
By then,
all the lights offstage will be out.

17:44.547 --> 17:46.466
You just need to watch Mu
and the others perform on stage.

17:46.466 --> 17:50.327
Got it. I will definitely live up to
The Perfect Voice Studio and do you proud.

17:51.827 --> 17:53.906
It's most important
to do justice to yourself.

17:55.466 --> 17:59.367
- Go for it!
- It's okay! We are all here for you.

17:59.907 --> 18:03.327
I cheered for you in Yangshuo,
now it's your turn to cheer for me.

18:03.387 --> 18:05.607
I'll be cheering you on
from under the stage!

18:05.986 --> 18:08.402
I'll join Xiaoxing and the others.

18:08.426 --> 18:10.766
Go for it! Goodbye.

18:12.706 --> 18:14.926
- Let's go, I'll accompany you.
- Okay.

18:16.706 --> 18:19.283
I'm still excited.

18:19.307 --> 18:20.186
- Sheng!
- So good!

18:20.186 --> 18:21.607
- You're amazing!
- Here!

18:23.186 --> 18:24.647
Come over here.

18:27.506 --> 18:29.226
Your song is really beautiful.

18:29.226 --> 18:32.682
It makes up for not going to Yangshuo
to see you perform last time.

18:32.706 --> 18:35.843
Let me tell you, this is the first time
my song is performed on stage.

18:35.867 --> 18:38.486
I'm more nervous
than when I was in Yangshuo.

18:38.827 --> 18:42.402
It was fantastic. You were great,
and the chief planner did an amazing job.

18:42.426 --> 18:44.446
And don't forget the chief director.

18:45.067 --> 18:46.603
I was really nervous just now.

18:46.627 --> 18:51.442
Up next is The Perfect Voice Studio,
presenting a dubbing clip.

18:51.466 --> 18:55.602
This clip is taken from last year's
dubbing drama, Memories of Jiangnan.

18:59.627 --> 19:00.627
IEMs.

19:01.787 --> 19:02.787
Let's go.

19:11.506 --> 19:15.887
Brother, Auntie wants to betroth me
to some man.

19:17.147 --> 19:18.726
I don't want to get married.

19:20.266 --> 19:22.386
If you can receive this letter,

19:22.946 --> 19:25.486
please find a way to get me out of this.

19:26.627 --> 19:27.966
If...

19:32.387 --> 19:34.206
If I must marry,

19:35.266 --> 19:37.966
I have decided
not to become a burden to you.

19:40.627 --> 19:43.287
If people find out
I am the sister of Shen Ce,

19:46.547 --> 19:49.206
I will certainly take my own life.

19:55.587 --> 19:59.127
Quick, someone wants to see you.
Your brother sent someone to pick you up.

20:08.706 --> 20:09.847
Brother.

20:14.186 --> 20:15.807
Do you still recognize me?

20:18.026 --> 20:21.926
I still love how you ran over by yourself
when you were a kid.

20:28.746 --> 20:30.526
I've got nothing.

20:31.226 --> 20:32.978
Only good news of winning battles.

20:33.534 --> 20:35.526
All good news of winning battles.

20:36.706 --> 20:40.926
They're about to marry me off
and all you do is war.

20:45.666 --> 20:46.847
You said,

20:47.666 --> 20:49.287
wherever I am,

20:50.026 --> 20:51.567
you will be there.

20:53.438 --> 20:55.807
It was all lie.

21:03.230 --> 21:07.486
My hard-earned reputation
is almost wiped out by you.

21:10.827 --> 21:13.843
Time is of the essence.
There is no time for lengthy explanations.

21:13.867 --> 21:16.966
- Can't you even stay for a while?
- No.

21:17.387 --> 21:22.087
- Then the next time...
- You can't stay there since it is exposed.

21:22.827 --> 21:25.127
You want to take me back
to the military?

21:26.147 --> 21:28.726
Yes, I'm taking you with me.

21:49.706 --> 21:51.166
We are home.

21:52.627 --> 21:53.847
Zhaozhao.

21:55.026 --> 21:56.807
They changed clothes too quickly!

21:57.827 --> 22:04.847
We joined the army to defend our homeland,
and to avenge our families.

22:05.787 --> 22:07.526
I am just like you.

22:08.062 --> 22:09.746
There's no difference.

22:10.302 --> 22:12.146
We all have the same concerns

22:12.666 --> 22:14.526
and the same aspirations.

22:15.547 --> 22:16.658
Today,

22:17.186 --> 22:22.446
I found my younger sister Shen Zhaozhao.
It is the greatest happiness of my life.

22:26.946 --> 22:30.002
This blade has been with me
for several years.

22:30.587 --> 22:33.074
It has slain emperor
and felled renowned generals,

22:33.627 --> 22:35.446
yet it has never had a name.

22:36.627 --> 22:41.446
- From now on, it shall be named Zhao.
- Amazing.

22:41.986 --> 22:43.926
May the fortune of this day

22:44.466 --> 22:46.066
reside with the blade.

22:46.627 --> 22:51.442
May my people in Chaisang
stay close to me like my kin.

22:51.466 --> 22:56.843
May Chaisang army guard the river for long
and remain undefeated in hundred battles.

22:56.867 --> 23:01.854
May the day come when we
finally drive out foreign tribes,

23:01.854 --> 23:06.006
and forever eliminate war and chaos.

23:07.746 --> 23:10.847
- So good!
- Good!

23:12.827 --> 23:15.047
- That's awesome!
- It's giving me goosebumps!

